{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/how-to-write-stories","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"fa9f8217-e504-5e8b-b196-6910a73f40a0","html":"<h1 id=\"how-to-write-stories\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-write-stories\" aria-label=\"how to write stories permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to write stories</h1>\n<p>一個 story 會 capture 一個 ui component 的 rendered state.\n這個 function 會根據給定的 arguments 回傳對應的 component state.</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p>Props 之於 Vue.js 的關係，會等同 Args 之於 Storybook。</p>\n<h2 id=\"where-to-put-stories\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#where-to-put-stories\" aria-label=\"where to put stories permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Where to put stories</h2>\n<p>component 的 story 會和 source code 放在一塊。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js\nButton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>stories<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>js</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"component-story-format\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#component-story-format\" aria-label=\"component story format permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Component Story Format</h2>\n<h3 id=\"default-export\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#default-export\" aria-label=\"default export permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Default export</h3>\n<p>storybook 是用 default export 來認出這是一個 story.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Button.stories.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Button <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./Button.vue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\ttitle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Components/Button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tcomponent<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"defining-stories\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#defining-stories\" aria-label=\"defining stories permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Defining stories</h3>\n<p>這邊會用 <em>named</em> exports 來定義 story 內的 state.</p>\n<p>官方建議這邊用 <code class=\"language-text\">UpperCamelCase</code></p>\n<p>下面例子是去 render 一個在 <code class=\"language-text\">primary</code> state 的 <code class=\"language-text\">Button</code>. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Button.stories.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Button <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./Button.vue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tcomponent<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\ttitle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Components/Button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Primary</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tcomponents<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\ttemplate<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;Button primary label=\"Button\" />'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>若有多個 state 需要呈現，那就延續著上面接著做下去。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Primary</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  components<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  template<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;Button background=\"#ff0\" label=\"Button\" />'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Secondary</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  components<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  template<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;Button background=\"#ff0\" label=\"😄👍😍💯\" />'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Tertiary</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  components<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  template<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;Button background=\"#ff0\" label=\"📚📕📈🤓\" />'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"using-args-推薦這用法\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#using-args-%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E9%80%99%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"using args 推薦這用法 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Using args (推薦這用法)</h3>\n<p>為 story 定義一個 master template 來優化上述的 code，這個 template 允許您傳入args。\n這樣可以減少為每個 story 編寫和維護的 effort 。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Button.stories.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Button <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./Button.vue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tcomponent<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Button<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\ttitle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Components/Button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//👇 We create a “template” of how args map to rendering</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Template</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> argTypes <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tcomponents<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Button <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tprops<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">keys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>argTypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\ttemplate<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;Button :background=\"background\" :label=\"label\" />'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//👇 Each story then reuses that template</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Primary <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">Template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nPrimary<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>args <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> background<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#ff0'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> label<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Button'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Secondary <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">Template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nSecondary<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>args <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>Primary<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> label<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'😄👍😍💯'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Tertiary <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">Template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">bind</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nTertiary<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>args <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>Primary<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> label<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'📚📕📈🤓'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Template.bind({})</code> 這是 copy 一份 template 的寫法。</p>\n<h2 id=\"ref\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ref\" aria-label=\"ref permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ref</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://storybook.js.org/docs/vue/writing-stories/introduction\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">How to write stories</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/how-to-write-stories","tagSlugs":["/tag/storybook/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-04-26T22:40:32.169Z","description":"記錄一下寫 storybook 時要注意哪些事項","tags":["Storybook"],"title":"How to write stories","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/6d93cbc4956a854d4c4369f0e281e7f3/42-line-bible.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/how-to-write-stories"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}